{"tid":653910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地產公司 女經理摑六下屬 數十人扮狗爬","createTime":"2018-05-05T07:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T07:58:45.000Z","uid":54373,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d11d919d95af7202c93500592839de8c6ab7de92","tid":653910,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180505/photo/0505-00178-016b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180505%2Fphoto%2F0505-00178-016b1.jpg&h=796b6cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地近日熱傳一段短片，內容是湖北宜昌一間地產公司六名男員工一字排開，被一名女主管逐一掌摑，另有數十名員工在地上扮狗爬。涉事公司胡姓負責人周四（3日）稱，事發於上月舉行的業務會，又指六名男員工因工作表現未如理想，主動要求被掌摑作懲罰。<br />\n公司負責人胡先生解釋，六名男員工未按照公司要求履職，例如未向客戶打電話等，僅僅是因為工作狀態太鬆散，與其業績毫無關係，女主管當時流淚掌摑員工。據被掌摑的譚姓男子稱，張姓女經理在月會上因不滿其工作態度和狀態，當眾批評包括他在內的男員工，男員工希望能通過「打臉」反省。他強調，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時張女不接受此建議，是男員工懇求了四五次，對方才有此舉動</span>，也打得不用力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180505/photo/0505-00178-016b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180505%2Fphoto%2F0505-00178-016b2.jpg&h=f7e46b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六名員工又表示，張女比他們大十多歲，平日無論工作和生活上都很關愛他們。在掌摑過程中，雙方都流了眼淚，未料團隊內的一次「批評」卻被網民誤解。<br />\n<br />\n或向發布者究責<br />\n胡先生表示，其公司目前有十多家門店、一百六十多名員工，在當地實力雄厚，而同行間競爭激烈。他指出，該公司至今對網傳短片不發聲，但不排除會追究發布短片者的責任。由於短片已廣傳，掌摑下屬的張姓女經理礙於壓力，已於周三（2日）離職回家休息。他續指，該公司會通過法律途徑維護當事員工的權益。<br />\n<br />\n網民斥丟男人臉<br />\n事件引起輿論熱議，不少網民批評被摑的男員工失去尊嚴︰「丟一個男人的臉」、「上個班，要這樣沒尊嚴嗎？ 」有人則批評這種企業文化可怕︰「這樣對待員工，吸引力在哪裏？」另有人不相信員工是主動要求被摑。<br />\n本報綜合報道"},{"pid":"9091eebfd10118cd05476def6362714fb471274a","tid":653910,"uid":37933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"條女係靚嘅話會變左另一種意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5beb3314a51be1bcee0b494056b1bd258c3c167","tid":653910,"uid":4575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"正呀，想見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c002fa2580eb2029f18ff0035641955322a77263","tid":653910,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9091eebfd10118cd05476def6362714fb471274a","tid":653910,"uid":37933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"條女係靚嘅話會變左另一種意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df49fd11cc037ff1c224659d77943b50620e4072","tid":653910,"uid":73262,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"無著皮衣+皮鞭， fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89eef6c2ca508b3e1d6219095858567a4280b5ef","tid":653910,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"M男 AV"},{"pid":"11903db14f73a714d44ce5b5d72c5fd1ade1170c","tid":653910,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee926a4a22942eb6eaa4b8cf83174ac7ac20cbe9","tid":653910,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"89afba7faa92f952154f2bc2a0ef3adb7b4f55af","tid":653910,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"3b895e306017f0c7058028c4e15779b6ab877a32","tid":653910,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64447aef739002e8e4b17594922102ac523320ad","tid":653910,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-0